{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And there, we met another man, and he was definitely Flemish, a Flemish accent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And then my Harry, the one who was supposed to do the whole thing, disappeared.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Never came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "He said, good luck, and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I did not have tickets to travel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I did not have a permit to travel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "I did have the fake ID, except I never had the chance to look at it, because he handed it to me under the table.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And I put it in my purse and never looked at it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "I didn't know either the name, who I was, where I was going-- anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And then I was on the train, and nobody was with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "You know, there were so many people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "They were just shoving you on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And around me were only Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And I was going, had no idea where.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "The only thing I remember, he said Roosendaal, which is a border-- Holland, Belgium border-- one of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "It was an incredible journey, because I was totally alone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "I had no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "I had enough change to buy a sandwich, not enough to go back home, even.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was hardly going to undo the coat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were Germans, Germans, Germans, Germans all over the place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I know that I went off the-- I went off the pla-- off-- off the train, sat-- sat alone in a station.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And trains were coming, and trains were going, and I was totally alone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had no idea what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then suddenly, somebody came and picked me up and pushed me on another train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the-- the Belgian guy by the name of John.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "John, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One of the people who traveled with us, a beautiful, elderly couple.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
